          "type": "text",
          "text": "function minCoinsDP(coins, amount) {\n  const INF = amount + 1;\n  const dp = new Array(amount + 1).fill(INF);\n  const prev = new Array(amount + 1).fill(-1);\n  dp[0] = 0;\n  for (let a = 1; a <= amount; a++) {\n    for (const c of coins) {\n      if (a >= c && dp[a - c] + 1 < dp[a]) {\n        dp[a] = dp[a - c] + 1;\n        prev[a] = c;\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  if (dp[amount] === INF) return { count: -1, coins: [] };\n  const out = [];\n  let a = amount;\n  while (a > 0) {\n    out.push(prev[a]);\n    a -= prev[a];\n  }\n  return { count: out.length, coins: out };\n}\n\nconsole.log(minCoinsDP([1, 3, 4], 6));\n// { count: 2, coins: [3, 3] }  <-- глобально оптимально"
